  11 May 2005; Gregorio Guidi <greg_g@gentoo.org> libmng-1.0.8-r1.ebuild:
  Fix bug #90514 by manually running autoreconf.

  22 Apr 2005; Diego Petten√≤ <flameeyes@gentoo.org> libmng-1.0.8.ebuild,
  libmng-1.0.8-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed dependency on autoconf/automake for version 1.0.8 (fixes #75824),
  cleaned up 1.0.8-r1 to use emake instead of just make.

*libmng-1.0.8-r1 (03 Apr 2005)

  03 Apr 2005; Gregorio Guidi <greg_g@gentoo.org> +libmng-1.0.8-r1.ebuild:
  Fix detection of liblcms.

  31 Oct 2004; Kito <kito@gentoo.org> libmng-1.0.8.ebuild:
  added ~ppc-macos

  30 Sep 2004; Travis Tilley <lv@gentoo.org> libmng-1.0.5.ebuild:
  fix sandbox violations for the current amd64 stable version of libmng as well

  09 Sep 2004; Paul de Vrieze,,, <pauldv@gentoo.org> libmng-1.0.8.ebuild:
  Fix sandbox error on amd64 (and possibly other platforms). In any case DESTDIR
  is preferred over prefix=... constructs.

  08 Sep 2004; Patrick Dawson <pkdawson@gentoo.org>
  libmng-1.0.4.ebuild, libmng-1.0.5.ebuild,
  libmng-1.0.7.ebuild, libmng-1.0.8.ebuild:
  Removed lcms from RDEPEND. Thanks to Christian Zoffoli <czoffoli@xmerlin.org>
  Closes bug #61191

*libmng-1.0.8 (06 Aug 2004)

